text: The V CELAC summit or 2017 CELAC summit was the fifth ordinary heads of state summit of the Community of Latin American and Caribbean States. It was held on 24 and 25 January 2017 in Punta Cana, Dominican Republic. == References == == External links == * Official declaration (Spanish) Category:2017 conferences Category:2017 in international relations Category:2017 in South America Category:2017 in the Caribbean Category:Conferences in the Dominican Republic Summit,2017
title: 2017 CELAC summit
